{"ID":270315, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"315\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs314.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs316.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 315<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">with the faith of the Saints,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> may say something instructive. It has gone abroad<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> that I proclaimed\n  myself no longer a prophet. I said it last Sabbath ironically: I supposed you would all understand.\n  It was not that I would renounce the idea of being a prophet, but that I had no disposition to proclaim\n  myself such. But I do say that I bear the testimony of Jesus, which is the spirit of prophecy.<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">There is no greater love than this, that a man lay down his life for his friends.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> I discover\n  hundreds and thousands of my brethren ready to sacrifice their lives for me.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The burdens which roll upon me are very great. My persecutors allow me no rest, and I find that\n  in the midst of business and care the spirit is willing, but the flesh is weak.<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> Although I was called\n  of my Heavenly Father to lay the foundation of this great work and kingdom in this dispensation,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span>\n  and testify of His revealed will<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> to scattered Israel,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> I am subject to like passions as other men, like\n  the prophets of olden times.<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">Notwithstanding my weaknesses,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> I am under the necessity of bearing the infirmities of\n  others,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> who, when they get into difficulty, hang on to me tenaciously to get them out, and wish me\n  to cover their faults. On the other hand, the same characters, when they discover a weakness in\n  Brother Joseph, endeavor to blast his reputation, and publish it to all the world, and thereby aid my\n  enemies in destroying the Saints.<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> Although the law is given through me to the Church,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> I cannot\n  be borne with a moment by such men. They are ready to destroy me for the least foible, and publish\n  my imaginary failings from Dan to Beersheba,<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> though they are too ignorant of the things of God,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span>\n  which have been revealed to me, to judge of my actions,<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> motives or conduct, in any correct manner\n  whatever.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The only principle upon which they judge me is by comparing my acts with the foolish\n  traditions of their fathers<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> and nonsensical teachings of hireling priests,<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> whose object and aim were\n  to keep the people in ignorance for the sake<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> of filthy lucre;<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> or as the prophet says, to feed\n  themselves, not the flock.<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> Men often come to me with their troubles, and seek my will, crying, Oh,\n  Brother Joseph, help me! But when I am in trouble few of them sympathize with me or extend to me\n  relief.<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> I believe in a principle of reciprocity,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> if we do live in a devilish and wicked world where\n  men busy themselves in watching for iniquity, and lay snares for those who reprove in the gate.<span class=\"footRef\">25<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113800\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113800)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113800)\">D&amp;C 43:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113952\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113952)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113952)\">D&amp;C 50:1<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110843\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110843)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110843)\">Rev. 19:10<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108825\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108825)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108825)\">John 15:13<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110603\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110603)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110603)\">1 Jn. 3:16<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108260\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108260)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108260)\">Matt. 26:35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108263\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108263)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108263)\">Matt. 26:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108368\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108368)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108368)\">Mark 14:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113064\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113064)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113064)\">D&amp;C 1:17,30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113402\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113402)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113402)\">D&amp;C 21:2<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114238\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114238)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114238)\">D&amp;C 64:33<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116601\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116601)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116601)\">D&amp;C 136:37-38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114528\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114528)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114528)\">D&amp;C 77:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">9. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115597\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115597)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115597)\">D&amp;C 109:67<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">10. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109103\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109103)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109103)\">Acts 14:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110397\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110397)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110397)\">James 5:17<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">11. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111349\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111349)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111349)\">2 Ne. 33:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109392\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109392)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109392)\">Rom. 15:1<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112107\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112107)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112107)\">Alma 31:30<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113764\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113764)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113764)\">D&amp;C 42:52<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110980\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110980)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110980)\">1 Ne. 13:9<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113117\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113117)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113117)\">D&amp;C 5:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113781)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113781)\">D&amp;C 43:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106382\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106382)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106382)\">1 Sam. 3:20<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109345\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109345)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109345)\">Rom. 10:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115512\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115512)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115512)\">D&amp;C 107:79-84<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112088\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112088)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112088)\">Alma 30:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115894\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115894)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115894)\">D&amp;C 123:7<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108747\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108747)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108747)\">John 10:12-13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112091\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112091)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112091)\">Alma 30:23,31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110475\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110475)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110475)\">1 Pet. 5:2<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">22. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107480\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107480)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107480)\">Ezek. 34:2-3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">23. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109077\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109077)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109077)\">Acts 11:29<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111570\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111570)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111570)\">Mosiah 4:26<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">24. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107879\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107879)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107879)\">Matt. 7:12<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">25. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107124\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107124)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107124)\">Isa. 29:20-21<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/d